      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just can't wait until i can get ahold of my doctor in the morning, i'm literally exhausted. i looked it up online and some people say it's totally fine in the second and third trimesters because the baby is already developed. can i just take one dose of the pseudoephedrine right now so i can finally get some sleep? it's just one pill, it shouldn't be a big deal, right?",
